  "synopsis": "In a different world with strong spiritual energy, Wang Baole, a warm and cheerful little fat man, saw through the illusion created by the teachers in the entrance examination of the famous school \"Dragon Taoist Academy\", and won high scores with his excellent performance, and obtained the \"Magic Department\". The quota of specially recruited students has since overcame obstacles and opened up his own way of upgrading. In the process of cultivating immortals and fighting monsters, he made a large number of close friends, and thus started a series of hilarious adventure stories.\n\n(Source: bilibili)",
